Welcome back.
You've improved quite a bit.

Yeah, I studied the recording and it made
a big difference in how I see things.

Will you watch it?

I'll definitely watch it!
As expected of Producer!

It's not perfect in just one try, right?
There are probably things to work on for today.
Haha, your enthusiasm is really something.

Because I want you to see lots of costumes too!
It's all part of being an idol!
